sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant EB as EventBridge
  participant CL as Collector Lambda (priority/discovery)
  participant X as X API
  participant EMB as Embedding API
  participant API as VPC API Lambda (/v1)
  participant DB as RDS PostgreSQL
  participant SLM as Summary LLM

  EB->>CL: Invoke scheduled run (15m/60m)
  CL->>X: Search tweets by query plan
  X-->>CL: Tweets + users + metrics
  CL->>CL: Normalize, dedupe, apply gates (omit/lang/noise), score significance
  CL->>API: POST /ingest/posts/batch (x-api-key)
  API->>DB: Upsert posts
  CL->>EMB: Embed selected posts
  EMB-->>CL: Vectors
  CL->>API: POST /ingest/embeddings/batch
  API->>DB: Upsert embeddings
  CL->>API: POST /ingest/runs
  API->>DB: Upsert pipeline_runs

  alt Discovery mode
    CL->>API: GET /feed for aligned windows
    API->>DB: Read window corpus
    CL->>SLM: Generate rolling_2h and rolling_12h narrative summaries
    CL->>API: POST /ingest/window-summaries/batch
    API->>DB: Upsert window_summaries
  end
